border-brand-teal/20 mb-4\">Cobertura Nacional · Ciudad Madero, Tamaulipas</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black uppercase text-brand-navy leading-tight tracking-tight mb-5\">Su aliado en<!-- --> <span class=\"text-brand-teal\">higiene y<br/>seguridad</span> <!-- -->industrial</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-lg leading-relaxed mb-7\">Fundamos nuestra empresa sobre tres principios:<!-- --> <strong>calidad, precios justos y servicio único.</strong> Soluciones rápidas y adaptadas a sus requerimientos.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg font-bold transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-brand-teal text-white hover:bg-brand-teal-dark h-12 px-8 text-base\" href=\"/productos\">Ver Catálogo <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#contacto\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg font-bold transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border-2 border-brand-teal bg-transparent text-brand-teal hover:bg-brand-teal hover:text-white h-12 px-8 text-base\">Solicitar Cotización</a></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-8 pt-6 border-t border-brand-light-blue-2\"><div><div class=\"text-2xl font-black text-brand-teal\">6+</div><div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide\">Categorías de producto</div></div><div><div class=\"text-2xl font-black text-brand-teal\">B2B</div><div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide\">Enfoque empresarial</div></div><div><div class=\"text-2xl font-black text-brand-teal\">100%</div><div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide\">Compromiso de calidad</div></div></div></div><div class=\"relative hidden md:block pl-8 pb-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden opacity-50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"140\" height=\"140\" viewBox=\"0 0 140 140\" fill=\"none\"><polygon points=\"70,0 140,0 140,70\" fill=\"#1D3F5E\" opacity=\"0.13\"></polygon><polygon points=\"100,0 140,0 140,40\" fill=\"#1D3F5E\" opacity=\"0.2\"></polygon></svg></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><svg width=\"44\" height=\"44\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><ellipse cx=\"22\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"18\" ry=\"22\" fill=\"#F5E200\"></ellipse><path d=\"M14 20 Q22 14 30 20 Q38 26 30 34 Q22 40 30 46\" stroke=\"#3BBFC0\" stroke-width=\"5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" fill=\"none\"></path><circle cx=\"42\" cy=\"18\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#1D3F5E\"></circle><rect x=\"40\" y=\"25\" width=\"4\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#1D3F5E\"></rect></svg><div><div class=\"font-black text-brand-teal text-base\">Servicios Integrales</div><div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">Perfil Corporativo</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-brand-light-blue flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-4 h-4 text-brand-teal\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path